           </div>
           <div class="articleListing__content">
            <h1 class="articleListing__headline" id="article-title-31" itemprop="headline">
             Language Resource Center opens in Stimson Hall
            </h1>
            <span class="articleListing__description" itemprop="description">
             <p>
              “We want this to be not only a place to practice other languages, but also a place to have encounters with other cultures.”
             </p>
            </span>
           </div>
          </a>
          <meta content="Thu, 11/29/2018 - 09:14" itemprop="datePublished">
