<div class="as-page__block">
 <div class="as-container">
  <div class="pictureText">
   <span class="field-image">
    <img alt="Speaking of Language Podcast logo" src="http://lrc.cornell.edu/sites/lrc/files/PodcastHome.jpg" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
   </span>
   <span class="field-description">
    <h2>
     <em>
      <a href="/podcast">
       Speaking of Language
      </a>
     </em>
     : The LRC Podcast
    </h2>
    <p>
     The LRC Podcast features weekly discussions about language learning and pedagogy, highlighting the work we and our partners do on campus and in the community. A typical episode is hosted by a member of the LRC and introduces new initiatives, teaching ideas, or general trends in second language learning and teaching. Look for new episodes with every semester at Cornell University. Listen to the most recent episode here, and binge on our
     <a href="/podcast">
      archived episodes
     </a>
     .
    </p>
    <iframe frameborder="0" height="500" src="https://castbox.fm/app/castbox/player/id1169802?v=4.1.0&amp;autoplay=0" width="100%">
    </iframe>
   </span>
  </div>
 </div>
</div>
